						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1458 (1536 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Records a gift of money by <hi rend="bold">Jñānanidhi-Uḍaiyar</hi> for a perpetual lamp in the temple for the merit of his preceptor <hi rend="bold">Lakshmīnārārāyaṇa-Uḍaiyar.</hi> The details of date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1458, Durmukhi, Dhanus, ba. Amāvāsyā, Tuesday, Kēṭṭai, correspond to 1536 A.D., December 12, Tuesday.</hi></p>						

